title: Turkey Bowling with My Father Cigars
itunes:title: Turkey Bowling with My Father Cigars
description: We're bowling with Turkey's live on the air with My Father Cigars. We've chosen the most perfect cigar rep, Jeremy Soares, to not only join us... but take over Mr Jonathan's seat! We light up the Flor De Las Antillas and La Duena.
